Authorization: Bearer <access_token>


Admin users can view, update, and delete all tasks.

Normal users can access only their own tasks.

Tasks are automatically linked to the logged-in user.

SQLite is used as the default database for simplicity.

This project is intended for learning and demonstration purposes.

Make sure migrations are run before accessing the admin panel or APIs.

API Endpoints

POST /api/auth/register/ – Register user

POST /api/auth/login/ – Login & get JWT

POST /api/auth/refresh/ – Refresh token

GET /api/tasks/ – List tasks

POST /api/tasks/ – Create task

PUT /api/tasks/{id}/ – Update task

DELETE /api/tasks/{id}/ – Delete task
